<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Connect DigiLocker</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Inter:400,600&display=swap');
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fbff 0%, #f3f6fa 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-top: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 40px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            padding: 0;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ececec;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .verification-banner {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #0369a1;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .verification-banner .check-icon {
            color: #059669;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .card-content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #111;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .action-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .action-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .action-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 16px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .action-icon.upload {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            color: #0369a1;
        }
        .action-icon.digilocker {
            background: #f3e8ff;
            color: #7c3aed;
        }
        .action-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .action-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .action-description {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .action-arrow {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-left: 12px;
        }
        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 0;
            background: #6b7280;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            margin: 24px 0 16px 0;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #4b5563;
        }
        .manual-link {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .manual-link:hover {
            color: #4b5563;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            padding-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .footer .brand {
            font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            display: block;
        }
        .footer small {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 2px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://dummyimage.com/180x40/cccccc/000000&text=Logoipsum" alt="Logoipsum" height="40">
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="verification-banner">
            <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
            You're verified.
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
            <h2>The Express Path to Verification</h2>
            <p>Save time by letting us pre-fill your details. Simply upload your latest résumé and connect to DigiLocker. We'll do the heavy lifting.</p>
            
            <div class="action-item">
                <div class="action-icon upload">📄</div>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <div class="action-title">Upload Your Résumé</div>
                    <div class="action-description">We'll parse your work and education history automatically</div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-arrow">→</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-item">
                <div class="action-icon digilocker">🔗</div>
                <div class="action-content">
                    <div class="action-title">Connect with DigiLocker</div>
                    <div class="action-description">Securely fetch your verified ID and Address proofs</div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-arrow">→</div>
            </div>
            
            <button class="btn" onclick="navigateToPrimaryDetails()">Review Your Details</button>
            <div class="manual-link">Nevermind, I'll Enter Manually</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="brand">Truebg</div>
        <small>Copyright © 2025 Truebg. All Rights Reserved.</small>
    </div>

    <script>
        function navigateToPrimaryDetails() {
            // Navigate to the primary_details page
            window.location.href = '<%= verifications_primary_details_path %>';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>